graph TD
    subgraph "Indexing Pipeline"
        Novel[Novel / Chapters] --> Chunking[Chunking Service]
        Chunking --> Chunks[TextChunks in PostgreSQL]
        Chunks --> Embedding[Embedding Service]
        Embedding --> VS[ChromaDB Vector Store]
    end

    subgraph "Search Pipeline"
        Query[User Query] --> EmbQuery[Query Embedding]
        EmbQuery --> Search[Semantic Search]
        Search --> VS
        VS --> Results[Top-K Evidence Chunks]
        Results --> Response[Search Response with Citations]
    end

    Chunks -->|embedding_status=failed| Retry[Retry Mechanism]

    style Novel fill:#e8f5e9
    style Chunking fill:#f3e5f5
    style Embedding fill:#f3e5f5
    style VS fill:#fff3e0
    style Results fill:#e1f5fe
    style Response fill:#c8e6c9
